overview: Muna and her grandmother are the last surviving member of their family. Munaâ€™s driving desire to provide a better life for herself and grandmother in the land of milk and honey, leads her smack dab into the hands of traffickers. That experience turns her once golden heart into one driven by stone cold revenge on those who stole her innocence. When secrets and betrayal complicate her strategy, she has a tough decision to make. Will she remain a prisoner of her past or allow love to set her free?
tagline: We are products of our past ...not prisoners of it.
title: Muna
